{%- comment -%}
  ============================================================
  TRUST BADGES  (the "unknown" social-proof / USP strip)
  - One FEATURED block (dark green card): icon + title +
    subtitle + overlapping customer avatars.
  - Any number of ITEM blocks (icon + title + subtitle) shown
    on a light background beside / below the featured card.
  - Layout differs per device (matches the reference):
      Desktop = featured card on the left, items in a row right.
      Mobile  = items row on top, featured card full-width below.
    Featured order (desktop side + mobile top/bottom) and the
    item flow direction are all configurable per device.
  - Device-split typography for featured title, featured
    subtitle, item title and item subtitle.
  ============================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign s = section.settings
  assign uid = section.id
-%}

{%- capture icon_json -%}
